1. To prepare the marinade, put all of the marinade ingredients in a blender. Blend on high speed until well combined. 2. Put 4 pieces of seitan on each of 12 metal or bamboo skewers. Place them in a large non足reactive bowl or baking dish, pour the marinade over them, and let marinate for at least 1 hour or up to overnight. 3. To prepare the Chimichurri Citrus-足Herb Sauce, put all of the chimichurri ingredients in a blender. Blend on high speed until well combined. Refrigerate until ready to use. 4. Prepare a charcoal, gas, or stove-top grill. Grill the skewers over medium-足high heat until well browned, about 5 to 7 minutes per side. Serve immediately, drizzled with the Chimichurri Citrus足Herb Sauce.